Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:16.22,0:00:22.78,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命運的轉輪不停地旋轉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.94,0:00:31.25,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我永遠注視著你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:35.03,0:00:40.38,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為何  我如此  三生有幸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:41.08,0:00:46.97,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每見到水平線  便有莫名哀傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.13,0:00:56.56,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遠遠地回首 過去的自己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:56.72,0:00:59.98,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無限感傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.89,0:01:06.86,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命運的轉輪不停地旋轉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:08.02,0:01:13.25,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能夠深入思考的只有  Mystery
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.49,0:01:19.75,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看  命中的良人就在那裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:19.91,0:01:26.47,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我  一直守候你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:26.62,0:01:35.02,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我  一直守候你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.88,0:21:45.04,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想嘗試如履薄冰般危險的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:45.18,0:21:51.69,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好希望心中描繪的夢想能夠成型
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.82,0:21:55.65,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Forever My Destiny
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:57.10,0:22:03.18,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太空船如果降臨在自己面前 我一定會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:03.32,0:22:10.02,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拋下朋友  離開地球展開旅行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:11.29,0:22:18.93,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說平靜的每一天就是幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:19.08,0:22:29.20,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我其實想逃  我害怕沒有你的每一天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:29.36,0:22:37.80,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像如履薄冰般  偷偷地  戀愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:37.94,0:22:44.47,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的心飛向你的速度比光速更快更遠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:44.58,0:22:48.42,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Forever My Destiny
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.80,0:00:02.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人與人的邂逅充滿了神奇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:02.40,0:00:03.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,各種刑案更是謎題重重
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:04.00,0:00:05.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能夠遇到你真的是太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.10,0:00:07.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天是悲哀的姐妹親情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:08.20,0:00:09.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,密室的謎題能解開嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:09.90,0:00:11.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唯一看透真相的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.50,0:00:12.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是一個外表看似小孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.50,0:00:13.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,智慧卻過於常人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.40,0:00:15.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他的名字是 名偵探柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.30,0:01:38.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在去沖野洋子演唱會的途中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:38.90,0:01:40.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弄丟了門票的大叔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.10,0:01:44.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在偶然間認識了青島全代小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.70,0:01:47.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她以開車去接她妹妹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.40,0:01:49.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為送給大叔門票的條件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.20,0:01:54.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是卻發現她妹妹青島美菜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.10,0:01:58.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陳屍於密室狀態的浴室內
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.90,0:02:03.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浴室的門窗全部用膠帶給封住了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.10,0:02:07.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,門的玻璃上還用膠帶弄出了"永別"的字樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.40,0:02:14.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後在膠帶上只查到美菜小姐一個人的指紋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.00,0:02:18.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔和目暮警官都認為是自殺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.00,0:02:21.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對 不是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.80,0:02:23.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是自殺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.90,0:02:25.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺害美菜小姐的兇手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.90,0:02:27.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是全代小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.20,0:02:32.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浴室密室事件(後篇)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.50,0:02:37.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目暮警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.10,0:02:39.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高木
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.40,0:02:41.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.20,0:02:43.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在便利商店那邊瞭解的情況如何
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.80,0:02:46.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚7點半左右
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.70,0:02:49.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她確實買了兩瓶浴室清潔劑和膠帶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.50,0:02:51.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有兩罐罐裝啤酒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.20,0:02:53.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罐裝啤酒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.50,0:02:56.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才在廚房我就看到兩個空罐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.90,0:02:58.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和安眠藥放在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.80,0:03:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在清醒的狀態下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.10,0:03:01.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該也不至於會自殺才對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.50,0:03:05.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼美菜小姐當時的神色怎麼樣呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.20,0:03:08.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們說她跟平常沒什麼兩樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.80,0:03:09.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.70,0:03:11.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是…什麼呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.20,0:03:14.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有 其實也沒什麼大不了的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.00,0:03:16.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.50,0:03:18.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看這案子一定是自殺錯不了的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.90,0:03:20.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是自殺 是自殺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.20,0:03:20.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,員警叔叔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.20,0:03:23.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說只是什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.60,0:03:25.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.40,0:03:29.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是便利商店店長他說了件奇怪的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.70,0:03:31.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他說美菜小姐在付錢的時候…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.10,0:03:33.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.60,0:03:34.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在幾點鐘了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.40,0:03:36.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.90,0:03:39.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很奇怪對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.90,0:03:40.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.00,0:03:44.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然現場是密室的話這案子就應該是自殺了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.70,0:03:47.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這件事情你還是告訴警官比較好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.60,0:03:51.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想這件事情能成為否定自殺…的證據…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.00,0:03:57.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個是什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.10,0:04:00.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你指那個貓眼嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.60,0:04:02.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我指再上面點的那個黑點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.90,0:04:08.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…這是血跡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.90,0:04:09.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,血跡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.70,0:04:16.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是這個地方怎麼會有血跡呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.80,0:04:18.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美菜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.00,0:04:21.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賢…賢二
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.20,0:04:23.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美菜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.90,0:04:25.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美菜自殺了是真的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.70,0:04:29.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過賢二你怎麼會知道的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.40,0:04:34.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我們通知他的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.70,0:04:37.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為剛好在美菜小姐的死亡推定時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.60,0:04:41.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏的錄音電話錄下了他的留言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.10,0:04:44.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後我們就調查了一下美菜小姐的通訊錄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.90,0:04:46.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以就請他到這裏來一趟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.10,0:04:48.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.80,0:04:50.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼美菜她會自殺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.50,0:04:52.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早知道那個時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.30,0:04:55.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我無論如何應該把窗戶打破衝進來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.80,0:04:58.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.80,0:05:00.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說你昨晚來過這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.20,0:05:03.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在我打電話過來之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.00,0:05:05.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是真的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.70,0:05:07.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.30,0:05:11.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我按了好幾次門鈴都沒人來開門
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.00,0:05:13.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後來我在玄關前面等了一會兒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.40,0:05:15.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是老樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.40,0:05:19.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就想她可能已經睡了於是就回去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.30,0:05:23.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因為這樣我才會著涼的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.80,0:05:24.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.10,0:05:26.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.30,0:05:28.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個血跡是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.90,0:05:31.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過這也未免太奇怪了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.50,0:05:33.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你既然知道這裏沒人怎麼還會來找她呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.00,0:05:35.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為已經約好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.50,0:05:37.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和她一起吃晚飯的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.20,0:05:40.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再加上美菜的電話錄音每次都一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.00,0:05:44.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算家裏有人也會處於打開的狀態
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.20,0:05:47.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.70,0:05:48.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快讓我見見美菜吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.90,0:05:50.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.50,0:05:52.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.30,0:05:56.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兇手用膠帶製造出密室的手法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.50,0:05:58.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及門上之所以會有血跡的原因
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.20,0:06:02.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有我一直覺得不對勁的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.30,0:06:04.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被我解開謎題了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.00,0:06:07.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是任何事物 現在都真相大白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.70,0:06:09.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,犯人絕對就是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.30,0:06:11.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,絕對就是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.60,0:06:12.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.90,0:06:14.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是全代小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.70,0:06:16.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她就是設計把我們引來這裏之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.40,0:06:19.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才完成這項密室殺人陰謀的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.00,0:06:22.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來現在她還不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.90,0:06:25.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她自己正握有決定性的證據
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.00,0:06:27.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是自殺是自殺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.00,0:06:30.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經肯定是自殺了啊 警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.40,0:06:34.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為案發現場的這間浴室
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.60,0:06:36.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論是門還是窗都從內側
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.30,0:06:39.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用膠布把縫隙貼了起來形成了完全的密室
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.60,0:06:42.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至於門上貼出的那句
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.40,0:06:44.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像是遺言所用的膠帶上面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.10,0:06:48.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也只能找出死去的美菜小姐的指紋這樣看來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.30,0:06:51.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這件案子也只有美菜小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.80,0:06:54.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己割腕自殺這種可能性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.00,0:06:56.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛利先生 那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.40,0:07:00.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全代小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.20,0:07:01.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個給你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.90,0:07:04.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是答應給你的今晚演唱會的門票
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.10,0:07:10.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不好意思啊 在這個時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.30,0:07:13.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.80,0:07:14.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就告辭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.00,0:07:17.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛利老弟 你還沒做筆錄呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.30,0:07:19.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊不要緊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.00,0:07:22.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等演唱會結束以後我會自己去警察局向你報到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.70,0:07:30.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛…毛利老弟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.70,0:07:42.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.40,0:07:43.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛利老弟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.80,0:07:44.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道說…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.80,0:07:46.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又要像以前一樣開始了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.70,0:07:47.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始 什麼意思啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.60,0:07:50.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才"砰"那一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.80,0:07:52.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經使我全部解開了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.40,0:07:57.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把浴室製造成密室 兇手所用的手法 
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.40,0:08:06.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼兇手啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.90,0:08:09.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才你自己不是還說這是自殺嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.70,0:08:13.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊呀 把我剛才的話忘了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.00,0:08:15.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是開玩笑的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.80,0:08:18.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.70,0:08:22.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實美菜小姐根本不是自殺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.90,0:08:24.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是被謀殺的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.40,0:08:29.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是被身為她姐姐的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.40,0:08:30.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全代小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.90,0:08:31.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你殺害的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.40,0:08:36.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全代小姐殺的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.80,0:08:39.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是真的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.70,0:08:42.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.80,0:08:44.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說…說什麼傻話啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.00,0:08:47.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎麼可能會殺害我的妹妹呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.00,0:08:48.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.40,0:08:50.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這間浴室是完全的密室
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.70,0:08:53.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才也是你們和我一起把門撞開的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.20,0:08:56.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這點你應該最清楚啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.50,0:08:57.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說啊 毛利老弟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.60,0:09:00.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然你說全代小姐是兇手的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.90,0:09:02.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就告訴我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.70,0:09:05.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她從這個用膠帶密封起來的密室裏逃脫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.60,0:09:07.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所使用的神奇手法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.80,0:09:09.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你管這個叫"神奇手法"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.10,0:09:12.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實根本就沒那麼誇張
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.40,0:09:18.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是誰都能做到的再簡單不過的方法了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.40,0:09:19.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼…警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.20,0:09:22.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在就請你把浴室的門關上好嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.20,0:09:27.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.70,0:09:29.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這扇門看上去你覺得怎麼樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.60,0:09:33.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要說怎麼樣啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.00,0:09:39.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.90,0:09:41.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.50,0:09:43.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些貼在浴室門內側玻璃的膠帶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.40,0:09:47.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果透過這扇門的玻璃看上去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.50,0:09:50.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會讓人感覺像是從浴室的內側貼上去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.10,0:09:54.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想這一點正好被全代小姐利用了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.70,0:09:57.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賢二先生說過美菜小姐有時候就算在家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.40,0:09:59.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也會把錄音電話打開的對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.20,0:10:01.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個和這個一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.40,0:10:04.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼這扇浴室的門
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.70,0:10:07.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從一開始就是開著的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.40,0:10:12.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕全代小姐是先讓她妹妹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.30,0:10:15.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,服下安眠藥睡著後把她拖到浴室裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.00,0:10:20.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再把浴室的門窗縫隙用膠帶全部貼了起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.00,0:10:22.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在割了她的手腕之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.50,0:10:28.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用力把門給拉開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.70,0:10:33.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走出去之後就這樣把門關上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.30,0:10:36.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為門的內側視覺死角
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.00,0:10:38.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算她一開始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.70,0:10:41.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就把內側的膠帶撕下來而進入了浴室
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.50,0:10:42.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不可能知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.10,0:10:46.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是什麼時候把膠帶撕下來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.80,0:10:48.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可…可是你們剛才進去的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.30,0:10:51.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是還很吃力的樣子嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.90,0:10:53.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因為我們被騙了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.30,0:10:56.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被全代小姐的演技
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.50,0:10:59.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.60,0:11:01.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 準備
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.60,0:11:05.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,握著門把手的就是全代小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.10,0:11:08.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她算準時機轉動門把手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.80,0:11:10.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我們產生是用力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.60,0:11:12.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才把門撞開的錯覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.40,0:11:15.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這間浴室是完全封閉的密室的錯覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.90,0:11:18.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣先入為主地進入我們的頭腦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.20,0:11:21.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.50,0:11:23.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這套運用心理製造錯覺的手法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.20,0:11:26.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果就她一個人在的話就無法成立了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.40,0:11:31.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以全代小姐才會把我們幾個帶到這裏來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.00,0:11:34.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此一來我們就可以成為因為感冒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.30,0:11:35.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而無法前來的賢二先生的替身了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.40,0:11:38.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可…可是毛利老弟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.10,0:11:40.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這間浴室裏的膠帶上面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.30,0:11:43.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只檢出死去的美菜小姐一個人的指紋啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.30,0:11:47.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且每段膠帶的切口上都
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.40,0:11:50.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以清晰地看到美菜小姐拇指和食指的指紋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.00,0:11:52.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這又是怎麼回事呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.00,0:11:54.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因為打包的關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.90,0:11:56.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打…打包
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.70,0:11:57.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全代小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.00,0:11:59.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在殺她妹妹之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.90,0:12:01.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先讓她幫忙打包
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.20,0:12:05.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把膠帶撕成一定長度後整齊地排列在桌子邊緣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.10,0:12:07.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.50,0:12:11.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她就用這些膠帶把浴室的門窗縫隙全部貼上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.50,0:12:13.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再拼出"永別"的字樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.40,0:12:15.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.70,0:12:17.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了不讓上面沾上指紋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.60,0:12:18.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些事情都是戴著手套做的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.40,0:12:20.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最好的證據
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.90,0:12:22.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是門邊那些曾經用過一次的紙箱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.40,0:12:26.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有桌子邊緣有曾經黏過膠帶的痕跡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.60,0:12:28.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想這些情況
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.40,0:12:31.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鑑識課的人員應該早就知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.50,0:12:33.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,順便
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.60,0:12:35.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯案必備的膠帶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.90,0:12:40.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和兩種浴室清潔劑也由妹妹代為購買
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.30,0:12:41.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全代小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.10,0:12:42.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是受你所託的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.80,0:12:46.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你原本是想在密閉了浴室之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.40,0:12:50.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再把兩種浴室清潔劑混合來殺了你妹妹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.70,0:12:52.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你妹妹買來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.00,0:12:55.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不能產生毒氣的相同種類的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.90,0:12:59.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在把浴室密封後才發現到這一點的你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.70,0:13:01.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就轉而用刀割了她的手腕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.00,0:13:04.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓她死於失血過多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.90,0:13:08.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想應該就是這樣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.30,0:13:10.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全代小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.80,0:13:16.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全…全代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.80,0:13:20.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.10,0:13:23.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照你所說的我的確有可能犯案
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.80,0:13:27.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前嫌疑最重的除了這個家原本的主人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.10,0:13:29.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是我這個做姐姐的也說不定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.00,0:13:31.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你看見了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.20,0:13:35.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是看見我用膠帶把這扇門的縫隙貼起來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.70,0:13:38.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是看見了我用刀割我妹妹的手腕了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.00,0:13:44.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你說得再怎麼精彩也只是空話罷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.00,0:13:46.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你什麼證據也沒有啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.00,0:13:49.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為這間浴室當時很有可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.70,0:13:51.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是用膠帶形成了密室的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.50,0:13:54.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣吧 警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.20,0:13:58.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎麼樣啊 毛利老弟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.00,0:14:00.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說得沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.00,0:14:02.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.80,0:14:07.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前你這種手法確實沒有明確的證據來證明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.00,0:14:09.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛利…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.50,0:14:10.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.20,0:14:14.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你殺害你妹妹所留下來的痕跡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.20,0:14:16.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在還留著呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.00,0:14:21.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且這是你無法開脫的決定性的證據
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.40,0:14:23.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.20,0:14:24.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賢二先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.40,0:14:27.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你剛才說過的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.40,0:14:28.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚你來過這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.60,0:14:33.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候按了多久的門鈴還記得嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.20,0:14:35.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我按了很長時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.40,0:14:37.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為到了約定的時間她還沒出現
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.20,0:14:40.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我想美菜她很可能在屋裏睡著了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.40,0:14:43.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.90,0:14:45.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是那樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.90,0:14:47.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.30,0:14:49.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼"那樣子"啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.20,0:14:51.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請你說明白點兒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.20,0:14:53.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全代小姐 我想那個時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.50,0:14:56.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你應該還在屋子裏對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.20,0:14:59.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.70,0:15:01.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你才會用玄關大門上的貓眼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.10,0:15:04.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看看來者到底是誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.40,0:15:08.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你忘了擦掉你妹妹濺到你臉上的血了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.60,0:15:12.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可以自己去看看玄關的大門
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.30,0:15:16.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上面還沾著你當時留下的血跡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.80,0:15:18.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯吧 高木警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.10,0:15:22.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.90,0:15:25.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算這樣 就算這樣又能代表什麼呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.30,0:15:28.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也可能是我妹妹她自己弄上去的血跡啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.40,0:15:32.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰在什麼時候弄上去的根本還不清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.50,0:15:34.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然把它拿來當證據
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.60,0:15:37.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這個名偵探真是徒有虛名啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.90,0:15:49.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.40,0:15:51.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也發現了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.40,0:15:58.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟玄關大門上附著的血跡形狀完全吻合的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.00,0:16:00.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你妹妹的血跡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.50,0:16:02.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全代小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.10,0:16:04.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在你頭上戴著的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.30,0:16:07.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那條黑色頭巾上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.80,0:16:13.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼可以請你解釋一下嗎 全代小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.20,0:16:18.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天才隨著CD附贈的這條頭巾上面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.00,0:16:22.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會沾有你妹妹的血跡呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.80,0:16:24.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但…但是毛利老弟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.90,0:16:26.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼會知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.70,0:16:29.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她在行兇的時候戴著這條頭巾的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.20,0:16:33.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這LOGO吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.90,0:16:37.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是頭巾上的LOGO
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.00,0:16:40.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這條頭巾上真正的LOGO應該是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.60,0:16:41.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,YoKo
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.40,0:16:43.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在第一個o上面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.30,0:16:46.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有用來表示重音的一橫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.10,0:16:48.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一橫沒有了就表示
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.90,0:16:51.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這上面一定沾了什麼東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.20,0:16:54.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想肯定是我妹妹濺上去的血
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.20,0:16:57.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變黑了之後才會這樣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.50,0:17:02.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你知道得很清楚啊 毛利先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.40,0:17:06.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是沒有拿到頭巾嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.10,0:17:10.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一開始我只是覺得哪裏不對勁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.40,0:17:13.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是卻一直沒有發覺這個關鍵點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.90,0:17:17.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過當我看到有著相同LOGO的鑰匙圈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.60,0:17:21.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和沾在大門貓眼旁邊的血跡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.70,0:17:22.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後就是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.80,0:17:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,賢二先生昨晚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.40,0:17:27.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來按過門鈴這件事情就讓我豁然開朗了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.70,0:17:29.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.70,0:17:32.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到無意間讓你看到的這個鑰匙圈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.70,0:17:34.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然成了破案的關鍵啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.90,0:17:40.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼說來 你承認罪行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.90,0:17:44.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要帶我去警察局或者是別的什麼地方都請便吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.70,0:17:47.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但…但是你為什麼要殺美菜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.50,0:17:50.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們姐妹倆的興趣愛好不是都一模一樣的嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.40,0:17:55.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許就是因為太一樣的緣故吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.60,0:18:00.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我妹妹美菜總是跟在我的後面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.70,0:18:03.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我喜歡同一個偶像明星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.40,0:18:06.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我買一樣的衣服和皮包
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.60,0:18:10.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連餐具和傢俱也都照著我的做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.30,0:18:12.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到這些
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.40,0:18:13.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最初我是很感動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.10,0:18:15.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟她是我妹妹嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.80,0:18:19.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 有一天我卻開始討厭起她來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.10,0:18:21.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妹妹她帶著純真無邪的表情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.20,0:18:23.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一面笑一面對我說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.60,0:18:26.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.50,0:18:29.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到這次我又跟你喜歡上同一個人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.30,0:18:30.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還向他表白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.10,0:18:33.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個人難道是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.80,0:18:34.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.30,0:18:38.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個人就是跟我交往了五年之久的你 賢二
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.50,0:18:43.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後來妹妹她還是橫刀奪愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.70,0:18:46.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果妹妹就和你訂婚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.70,0:18:50.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我竟然淪落到要離開這個家的地步
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.10,0:18:54.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才想到要除掉她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.60,0:18:59.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除掉那個把我一切都奪走的惡魔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.90,0:19:02.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要她從我眼前馬上消失
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.30,0:19:04.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不是這樣的 全代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.80,0:19:08.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提出結婚的其實是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.80,0:19:11.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然她拒絕了我好幾次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.50,0:19:13.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她一直勸我別跟她在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.70,0:19:15.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要和姐姐你重歸於好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.10,0:19:17.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你騙人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.50,0:19:20.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她跟我說是她一直纏著你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.60,0:19:22.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她之所以會這麼說是因為
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.70,0:19:24.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是接受我求婚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.20,0:19:26.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的唯一條件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.30,0:19:27.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是因為我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.60,0:19:29.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然選擇了她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.70,0:19:31.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以她不想讓你知道這件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.00,0:19:34.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你的自尊心一向就比別人強
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.50,0:19:39.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要再說了好不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.00,0:19:43.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像她那種自私的人怎麼會為我著想呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.90,0:19:45.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.00,0:19:49.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也無法得知你妹妹的真實想法了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.90,0:19:52.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過可以肯定的是你妹妹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.40,0:19:54.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常地重視你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.90,0:19:58.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.70,0:20:01.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你懂什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.80,0:20:04.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為便利商店的店長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.60,0:20:06.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他這麼說過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.60,0:20:09.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你妹妹在付錢的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.70,0:20:13.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾將其中的一種浴室清潔劑特地換掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.20,0:20:16.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能是為了避免產生氯氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.70,0:20:19.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才把它們換成相同種類的東西 
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.80,0:20:23.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了要 保護你的性命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.20,0:20:27.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎麼會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.20,0:20:32.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說謊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.70,0:20:34.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美菜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.20,0:20:39.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美菜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.20,0:20:42.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快跟我說這不是真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.60,0:20:43.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美菜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.60,0:20:44.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美菜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.20,0:20:46.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美菜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.60,0:20:48.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美菜快回答我啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.60,0:20:52.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美菜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.90,0:20:56.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美菜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.80,0:21:03.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一開始的擔心演變成憎惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.80,0:21:06.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後產生了殺意的這件案子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.30,0:21:10.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在兇手懺悔的痛哭聲中結束
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.30,0:21:13.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那對一模一樣的杯子和牙刷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.70,0:21:17.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣靜靜地擺在鏡子前面訴說著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.70,0:21:21.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些過去曾經的美好回憶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.40,0:21:24.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許早就被人遺忘了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:02.90,0:23:04.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洋子小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:05.40,0:23:08.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最愛的洋子小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:09.10,0:23:10.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛利先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:10.70,0:23:12.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你果真來看我的演出啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:13.30,0:23:14.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是當然的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:14.90,0:23:15.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洋子我好高興哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:18.90,0:23:22.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啦 洋子小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:23.80,0:23:25.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這麼多粉絲面前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:25.80,0:23:27.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣子不太好啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:27.60,0:23:29.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不太清楚大叔到底夢到了什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:29.10,0:23:31.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡著了還在笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:32.00,0:23:34.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是夢到了去看演唱會了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:35.00,0:23:36.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要這樣啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:40.60,0:23:42.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洋子小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:55.50,0:23:57.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她好像很緊張的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:58.00,0:23:59.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底是誰呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:59.40,0:24:00.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個頭髮長長的男人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:04.80,0:24:05.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼這個東西…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:07.20,0:24:08.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:08.60,0:24:09.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:10.30,0:24:13.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謎的狙擊者殺人事件(前篇)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:14.70,0:24:16.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan's HINT
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:17.20,0:24:18.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聚光燈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:19.30,0:24:20.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下一回是原創的故事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:20.70,0:24:21.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:22.00,0:24:23.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原創是什麼意思啊
